n o t e s

As the excitement for another season of Caribbean
carnivals and the new songs that will run the road
gets under way, Soca Arena presents the best and
latest offerings from some of Soca's hottest
producers and artists. By popular demand, VP
Records kicks off the Soca Carnival season with
Soca Arena, a collection of new full length jump up
winners with an extended mega mix .
